snippet: Usain Bolt, the world 100- and 200-meter record-holder, made a surprise 2015 season debut in Kingston, Jamaica, running the anchor leg in a 4x100 relay heat victory at the Gibson Relays.
abstract: Jamaican sprinter Usain Bolt makes surprising 2015 season debut in 4x100 relay at Gibson Relays.
lead_paragraph: Usain Bolt, the world 100- and 200-meter record-holder, made a surprise 2015 season debut in Kingston, Jamaica, running the anchor leg in a 4x100 relay heat victory at the Gibson Relays.
